And to achieve a certain profit,

40:09.000 --> 40:11.000
you need to understand the sales volume

40:12.000 --> 40:14.000
that a company needs to achieve this profit.

40:15.000 --> 40:17.000
That is, what is the minimum sales volume

40:18.000 --> 40:20.000
that we need to achieve to get the desired profit.

40:21.000 --> 40:22.000
Pay attention to the formula.

40:23.000 --> 40:25.000
Here we use the following quantities.

