Constant company costs, target profit and return.

40:29.000 --> 40:31.000
You remember that the return is the difference

40:31.000 --> 40:33.000
between the price of the product and the variable costs

40:34.000 --> 40:35.000
for the production of this product.

40:36.000 --> 40:38.000
Knowing these four quantities,

40:39.000 --> 40:40.000
a company can calculate

40:41.000 --> 40:43.000
what sales volume it needs to achieve

40:44.000 --> 40:46.000
to get the desired profit at this price level

