this indicator that we calculate,

50:22.000 --> 50:23.000
the higher the probability

50:24.000 --> 50:25.000
that the buyer will buy our product.

50:26.000 --> 50:27.000
To increase the share of the shelf,

50:28.000 --> 50:29.000
