Another option

50:54.000 --> 50:55.000
is to create

50:56.000 --> 50:57.000
a modification of the product.

50:58.000 --> 50:59.000
Let's say, when a company

51:00.000 --> 51:01.000
offers several modifications

51:02.000 --> 51:03.000
of a product under one brand,

51:04.000 --> 51:05.000
the share of the shelf

51:06.000 --> 51:07.000
is usually higher.

