This factor can also be a source

51:44.000 --> 51:45.000
of possible problems.

51:46.000 --> 51:47.000
If we find that

51:48.000 --> 51:49.000
the absence of the product

51:50.000 --> 51:51.000
in the warehouse is high,

51:52.000 --> 51:53.000
we need to improve

51:54.000 --> 51:55.000
the system of our product movement,

