Please note that

53:02.000 --> 53:03.000
the coefficient of repeated purchases

53:04.000 --> 53:05.000
is the ratio of the number of buyers

53:06.000 --> 53:07.000
who tried the product

53:08.000 --> 53:09.000
and not all potential buyers.

53:10.000 --> 53:11.000
As a rule,

53:12.000 --> 53:13.000
these coefficients are calculated

53:14.000 --> 53:15.000
by the results of marketing research.

53:16.000 --> 53:17.000
A survey is conducted

53:18.000 --> 53:19.000
to determine

53:20.000 --> 53:21.000
whether potential buyers

53:22.000 --> 53:23.000
intend to buy a certain product

53:24.000 --> 53:25.000
and the percentage of buyers

53:26.000 --> 53:27.000
who buy it

53:28.000 --> 53:29.000
is determined

53:30.000 --> 53:31.000
by the coefficient of repeated purchases.

