57:12.000 --> 57:13.000
the total estimated volume of sales

57:14.000 --> 57:15.000
consists of the estimated volume

57:16.000 --> 57:17.000
of trial purchases

57:18.000 --> 57:19.000
and the estimated volume of repeated purchases.

57:20.000 --> 57:21.000
Knowing the coefficients of trial purchases

57:22.000 --> 57:23.000
and the coefficients of repeated purchases,

57:24.000 --> 57:25.000
we can calculate

57:26.000 --> 57:27.000
the estimated volume of sales.

