You see that for each show we calculated the impression.

01:17:51.000 --> 01:17:52.000
That is, how many contacts

01:17:53.000 --> 01:17:55.000
of the target audience were there for each show.

01:17:56.000 --> 01:17:57.000
If we had 3 impressions,

01:17:57.000 --> 01:17:59.000
and the target audience is 5 people,

01:18:00.000 --> 01:18:01.000
then this is 60%.

01:18:02.000 --> 01:18:05.000
That is, the rating point for the first show is 60%.

