01:20:23.000 --> 01:20:25.000
The following metrics have a more general nature.

01:20:26.000 --> 01:20:28.000
They reflect the effectiveness of marketing as a whole.

01:20:29.000 --> 01:20:31.000
Surely, many of you have encountered

01:20:32.000 --> 01:20:33.000
the indicators of profitability and sales.

01:20:34.000 --> 01:20:35.000
This indicator is calculated as

01:20:36.000 --> 01:20:37.000
net profit as a percentage of revenue.

01:20:38.000 --> 01:20:39.000
Profitability of investments

01:20:40.000 --> 01:20:41.000
or return on investment

01:20:42.000 --> 01:20:43.000
is also probably familiar to many.

01:20:44.000 --> 01:20:45.000
Here we have

01:20:46.000 --> 01:20:47.000
the indicators calculated as net profit

01:20:47.000 --> 01:20:49.000
as a percentage of our investments.

01:20:50.000 --> 01:20:53.000
But there is a specific indicator in marketing.

01:20:54.000 --> 01:20:56.000
This is profitability of marketing investments.

01:20:57.000 --> 01:20:58.000
It is called RMI.

01:20:59.000 --> 01:21:01.000
Here we take the conversion of sales volume

01:21:02.000 --> 01:21:04.000
obtained precisely due to marketing activity,

01:21:05.000 --> 01:21:06.000
that is, the volume of sales

01:21:07.000 --> 01:21:08.000
that would not have been without marketing,

01:21:09.000 --> 01:21:11.000
multiply by the return,

01:21:12.000 --> 01:21:13.000
and you remember that this is

01:21:14.000 --> 01:21:15.000
the difference in price and variable costs,

01:21:15.000 --> 01:21:17.000
and subtract from this value

01:21:18.000 --> 01:21:19.000
the costs of marketing.

01:21:20.000 --> 01:21:22.000
In fact, this is how we calculate

01:21:23.000 --> 01:21:24.000
the conversion of our profit

01:21:25.000 --> 01:21:27.000
obtained as a result of marketing activity.

01:21:28.000 --> 01:21:30.000
And we divide this value by the costs of marketing.

01:21:31.000 --> 01:21:34.000
The higher the RMI of the investment in marketing,

01:21:35.000 --> 01:21:36.000
the more effective

01:21:37.000 --> 01:21:39.000
the marketing activity of the company.

